snippet.title: Mega64: Doug Huggem
snippet.description:
Originally ran on Gametrailers.com in February 2011. Featuring Jon St. John!

Also features an introduction to who Mega64 actually is, at the beginning. We were asked to do this so people on Gametrailers might actually know who we were.

Go to Gametrailers.com and see more of our exclusive videos there today!

http://mega64.com
